summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller for and on behalf of the City of Seattle, to make, execute and deliver to August P. Hohman, a quit-claim deed to a portion of the southwest one-quarter (1/4) of the southwest one- quarter (1/4) of Section Twenty-one (21), Township Twenty-five (25) North, Range Four (4) East, W.M.
